Benefits.heading: Smart Card
Benefits.title: Benefits
bullets: Freedom of choice of originating and destination station.
Minimum discount of 10% on every journey.
Used in DTC, Cluster & Metro feeder buses.

Purchase.title: Purchase from
bullets: Customer Care Centre smart card vending machine for 150/- (50/- security deposit + 100/- add value).

Recharge.title: Recharge
Recharge.subtitle: At Customer Care Centre
Recharge.smsRechargeSubtitle: SMS for ICICI bank account holders
autoTopUp: Issued by selected banks (check with your bank).
Auto top up through automatic fare collection gate.
Value of 200/- will be added when balance of card goes below 100/-
Recharge.maxAmount: Maximum amount in Smart Card shall be 3000/-
Recharge.validity: Validity  10 years from date of purchase or date of last recharge.

Discount.title: Discount
bullets: Additional discount of 10% is given if commuter enters into the paid area during off-peak hours*.
Discount.additionalNote: *Additional discount will be available from Monday to Saturday except on National Holidays.

content.title: Types of cards
bullets: Three day card - For 500/- (450/- + 50 refundable security).

content.title: Refund
bullets: Amount in tourist card shall not be refunded.
Security deposit shall be refunded after surrendering readable and physically OK card.

NationalCommonMobilityCard.heading: National Common Mobility Card
NationalCommonMobilityCard.subtitleOne: Use Rupay debit card Issued by banks for travel. (check with your bank).
NationalCommonMobilityCard.subtitleTwo: Please enable this card at first time from customer care.

bullets: Freedom of choice of originating and destination station.

content.title: Recharge
bullets: At Customer Care Centre through linked bank account.
